{"tid":1791642,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"討論割唔割已經證明有人仲未接受到武裝升級。致勇武。","createTime":"2019-12-21T04:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T12:43:18.000Z","uid":158270,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c2838270b6cd98c1d77461d70a7f73bb5a0305b6","tid":1791642,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:20:35.000Z","msg":"直至到佢哋發現有槍可以令「香港人報仇」、「黑警死全家」甚至「五大訴求缺一不可」由口號變成現實為止。<br />\n暴力潔癖唔會帶嚟勝利；畫面靚唔會阻到秋後算賬；我估依家連陣地戰都唔會改變到大搜捕嘅計劃。只有武裝起嚟，我哋先可以確保有反抗能力。<br />\n<br />\n不過我同埋其他人點諗武裝升級其實對你哋都唔重要。我哋冇行動力，淨係識出把口，結局就只有被消滅，或者跟隨你哋嘅路。我哋嘅猶豫同懦弱注定我哋會失去反抗力量。我哋仲喺度講割唔割，足以證明我哋同大勢完全脫節。"},{"pid":"7a291282d833498d29bb5e467d27bdf0b46bc5a7","tid":1791642,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"練習練習"},{"pid":"7c1acab415ff72ea4efb07de114e3f74582fabb0","tid":1791642,"uid":3358,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:21:50.000Z","msg":"次撚次爭住幫人出黎認做咩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6d7fc6aea02808d09d0456ee8d986cb53dfd04","tid":1791642,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:22:18.000Z","msg":"唔割 唔等於 狗隊話你有飛機大炮原子彈都認<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2URZO3u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2URZO3u.png&h=a0d2c640&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53898a552a1866f3e5d77ffa3ff70a463f212ce5","tid":1791642,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac6d7fc6aea02808d09d0456ee8d986cb53dfd04","tid":1791642,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:22:18.000Z","msg":"唔割 唔等於 狗隊話你有飛機大炮原子彈都認<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img